text: Novosyuryukayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Meshchegarovsky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 145 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 54 km from Maloyaz, 3 km from Mursalimkino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Novosyuryukayevo
